title: Diffusion Index, Plant and Equipment Expenditures, Actual and Expected, 19-22 Industries, Four Quarter Span for United States
notes:
This Index Is Based On Industry Components Listed In "Plant And Equipment Expenditures Of Business," Office Of Business Economics Business News Report. Coverage For 1947-February 1951 Is Twenty-Two Companies; For March 1951-February 1954 Is Nineteen Companies; For 1954-1958 Is Twenty Companies. Source: G.H. Moore, Business Cycle Indicators, Vol. 2, NBER, P. 170
